                  <msContents>
                     <summary/>
                     <msItem xml:id="p2_i1">
                        <locus from="165a" to="214a">Fols 165a–214a</locus>
                        <title type="supplied">Commentary on the Gospel of John.</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝʿǝz</textLang>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ፈጣሪ፡ ሕያው፡ ቀዳማዊ፡ ዘሀሎ፡ ወይሄሉ፡ እስከ፡ ለዓለም፡ ንወጥን፡ እንከ፡ ብስራተ። ዮሐንስ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ፈጻሜ፡ ብስራት፡ ክቡር፡ ነባቤ፡ መለኮት። በቀዳሚ፡ ኮነ፡ ቃል፡ ሕልወ።
                        </incipit>
                        <note>Same commentary on the Gospels as British Library Orient. 731 and British Library Orient. 732; Named sources include John Chrysostom, Ephrem, Athanasius, Gregory Theologus, and Isho'dad of Merv
                           
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                  </msContents>
